_sText: This is a a Gun Game Map in the Location of a Fantasy Area in Middle East. The Textures are Dust like. There are 2 Ways. The first in the open Area, and the second in the close Area. The close Area is a Overpass Tunnel with Windows and cross the open Area. You can play with 32 Player. I hope you like it.
